      "text": "Smello captured the incoming `POST /api/checkout` (Django middleware) and two outgoing calls. The request body has `\"amount\": 4999` but the Stripe charge was created with `amount=0`. The `checkout` view reads `data[\"total\"]` instead of `data[\"amount\"]`."
